title: Person of Interest S2E17 Ending Part 1
author: Morgs K
comment: Amazing episode. One of my favorite. So creepy and eerie but from this point and on the acting is amazing.
S2E17 is one of my favorite episodes, Jim and Michael did a great job as always, but Luke Macfarlane's acting makes this episode even more special.
0:24 - first watched this episode in the early hours of the morning and almost shrieked at this bit. XD
Great ending again thx for uploading it !

I love this episode but man I could tell the identity killer was Fahey from the beginning. From when John first met him when he said put your hands up show me your badge I knew that no FBI agent was that unprofessional.
